overview: Psalty and his pals Woofer and Tweeter invite youngsters to dance and sing in praise of the lord with Psalty's Funtastic Praise Party. Full of fun songs, movement, and hundreds of puppets, the party really gets started when Midi makes a surprise appearance.
tagline: Your kids and grandkids will love these classic titles as much as you did.
title: Psalty's Funtastic Praise Party
